    Create list of required parameters for ProxyErrorSpectrum

    GetSpecPars.Rd

    Returns a list of arguments to ProxyErrorSpectrum where arguments in the call replace the defaults. Default values are returned for all arguments not in the call.

    Usage

    GetSpecPars(proxy.type, ...)

    Arguments

    proxy.type

    "Mg_Ca", "T_deg_Mg_Ca", "T_deg_Uk37", "Uk37" or "d18O"

    ...

    Arguments to ProxyErrorSpectrum, e.g. delta_t = 1000

    Value

    A list of arguments to ProxyErrorSpectrum

    Examples

    if (FALSE) {
GetSpecPars()
}
GetSpecPars(proxy.type = "Mg_Ca")
